<figureCitation box="[1336,1423,1389,1415]" captionStart="FIGURE 41" captionStartId="150.[151,255,1990,2013]" captionTargetBox="[170,1423,960,1973]" captionTargetId="figure@150.[151,1436,942,1990]" captionTargetPageId="150" captionText="FIGURE 41. Distribution maps of Geonoma triandra, G. triglochin, G. trigona, and G. umbraculiformis." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3538445" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3538445/files/figure.png" pageId="149" pageNumber="150">Fig. 41</figureCitation>
